long_description: english:living better | vivre mieux nutritional supplements based on science and research is the philosophy that dr. gustavo bounous held as a medical doctor, researcher, and creator of immunocal. dr. bounous believed that nature holds many secrets for optimal health. how to unlock these secrets and prove their effectiveness became his passion. originally patented in the u.s. and canada over 20 years ago, today immunocal enjoys global recognition as the gold standard supplement in raising glutathione through natural protein ingestion. immunocal is listed in two of north america's most trusted medical references: the physician's desk reference (pdr) and the canadian compendium of pharmaceuticals and specialties (cps). one vision, one teamvisionwith our customers, consultants and employees at the heart of what we do, immunocal will become the nutritional choice worldwide. missionat immunotec, our mission is to provide high-quality scientifically-based nutrition and wellness products which enhance quality of life and performance. we thrive by empowering people to share an exceptional network marketing opportunity accessible to everyone. we commit to continued growth and prosperity for our consultants, employees and shareholders. valuesa fun atmosphere in all we undertake. a work environment grounded in teamwork and the achievement of shared goals. a commitment to service excellence, always seeking to exceed expectations. continuous improvement in all aspects of the immunotec experience. a culture that embodies integrity, generates respect, and reinforces trust. français:notre mission est de fournir des produits de nutrition et de bien-être de haute qualité, fondés sur des bases scientifiques, qui améliorent la qualité de vie et les performances .
